          ],
          "en.sarwar": [
            "3. Ali ibn Muhammad has narrated from Salih ibn abu Hammad from ibn abu ‘Umayr from and ibn Faddal from various people from abu Ja’far and abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who have said the following: “Abu Ja’far (a.s.) has said, ‘It is to disbelieve Allah, the Most Great, to disown one’s lineage even though it is very lowly. ’” "
